  <description><![CDATA[<p>Its panoramic position allows the hotel superb views across the bay or Taormina, this traditional hotel has mature gardens that encompass the pool and terraces.</p>
<p>The historic centre of Taormina is only a short walk where you can visit the ancient Greek Amphitheatre and shops of the town.</p>
<p>The Pirandello is open in the winter months and La Terraza restaurant through the summer allowing you enjoy the cooling breezes while you dine on its ‘sky terrace’</p>]]></description>
